{"tid":1583881,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[認真分析檢討Po][行動]討論著黑衫&癱瘓對家文宣手法","createTime":"2019-09-21T00:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T00:32:53.000Z","uid":63045,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c273dfd25e9afccebe5eceb51c3ca910749bbe91","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:27:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1.觀察</span><br />\n發覺對家好鍾意用一種手法：就係將示威者歸類，再邊緣化，小眾化，將示威同市民切割<br />\n例如2014稱呼做黃絲<br />\n依加叫做黑衣人<br />\n泰國叫黃衫軍<br />\n法國叫黃背心<br />\n<br />\n之後不停用假新聞抹黑著黑衫既人，嚴厲對待黑衣人，等啲游離支持者同黑衫劃清界線，同埋揾人著住黑衫去破壞示威者國際形象<br />\n<br />\n聽過啲無腦藍絲同事係街見到人著黑衫都對條友有偏見，話人係示威者，原因係對家文宣都不斷叫示威者做黑衣人，大陸演練又係揾黑衣人做target<br />\n<br />\n再諗番起前排個幾位成日Twitter開po既外國人，係咁建議我地唔好再用Hong Kong Protesters, 要用HongKonger去稱呼自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 建議</span><br />\n有兩個方法應對，Be water<br />\n一係大家乜色衫都著，二係每次著唔同色既衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 效果</span><br />\n1. 對家超過一半文宣要從新做過，打亂現行緊既計劃<br />\n2. 向外展示示威係市民訴求，大家都係平民，有咩事就係警察/黑社會打平民<br />\n3. 對家無得輕易target 示威者，草木皆兵<br />\n<br />\n記住，我地打長期戰，要不停檢討同埋變通，用死一招對方點要會拆到，佢改善唔到自己形象，唯有就令示威者形象比佢差，掩蓋咗佢，14年其中一個敗因都係對家出依招<br />\n<br />\n當然有啲活動例如十一大家認為有需要，都可以照著黑色，但其他活動就以平民裝，咩色都著<br />\n<br />\n一齊轉個靚彎等班垃圾重新諗過計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed88a63519e0c70a86395b0fa1e0207b0fbf91e","tid":1583881,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:27:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"64e384c38e4b7298b1c8a9904bb7138d0cedbec6","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:27:56.000Z","msg":"[連登平行世界]知道有BirdFoldingChallenge既請舉手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583663</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推"},{"pid":"a1bce9ac331d628ea133baf57c73fa89d4b13916","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:28:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faa63407a1b7a25b02192c159f3b9ad8402bc73f","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:29:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a868d79fbfdb9c27c5f65cf8a63fdfb5e991c40b","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:29:44.000Z","msg":"太長無人睇？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5afce28aa299aea72073ceaae5d6ccbed2807b","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:29:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3eca6d748c799f67e34d92f20bccc498858be409","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:30:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9af57e1aa763bce5f5d822a4c88ece84acdc643b","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:30:36.000Z","msg":"推，要變通先會進步"},{"pid":"7856ff4c87bf2b48983914539fb7e88095516940","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:30:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"152443333519c481a9cf4194660c3e4cd1fd3ef6","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25d23e5469e955e6f002ea9d0c8177a29a5569dc","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:31:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db09bf6227403028014b18825f69e30420518a88","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53f5d3d7a369ad10a1a53581c27eb2880adcd765","tid":1583881,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:3